{
  "texts": [
    "Alternatively, one might try several data augmentation methods.",
    "As a result, GAI models may be less susceptible to bias due to data noise.",
    "Debiasing methods are another option since they may be used to either discover and eliminate biased features from the data or to alter the model's weights to lessen the bias (Taly et al., 2019; Abdel-Aty and Gould, 2022).",
    "Future applications of GAI models are anticipated to be bolstered by few-shot learning methodologies paired with large-scale pre-trained CLMs (Gao and Coley, 2020).",
    "The practical usefulness of CLMs in drug development is also likely to grow as their capacity to suggest synthesizable compounds is enhanced (Krenn et al., 2022)."
  ]
}